        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Total production volume of hydraulic cement in Tunisia in 2019: 8'096'000 metric ton. Source: USGS (2019). U.S. Geological Survey, Minerals Yearbook Annual Tables, 2019. Available at: https://www.usgs.gov/centers/national-minerals-information-center/cement-statistics-and-information 

The share of Portland SR3 in the market is 11.8%. This share is based on the annual production from the cement manufacturer.
